==How to use WikiAudio==


[[file:one.png|18px]]  Use the search field to find any information you are looking for that pertains to sound science,technology or art.


[[file:two.png|27px]]  If you can't find the information you are looking for then submit a question or request using the grey ''Submit Question'' icon (upper right of screen)


[[file:three.png|42px]]When questions (or requests) are answered correctly, the answers will be turned into article pages on the main site by the moderator (or other users). Hence the most relevant information pertaining to the answer of each question is ''conveniently'' organized for future use and reference.
